    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are currently functional, but you may notice a minor oil seep and the suspension feels a bit soft over bumps. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the roof, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a few non-functional plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who is willing to handle some upcoming maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups.",
