    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and its signature 8,400 RPM redline. This example maintains excellent compression and features a precise 6-speed manual transmission paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback expected from this chassis. Key preventative maintenance, including throttle actuators and a recent fluid analysis, confirms the integrity of the powertrain. A robust performance machine ready for the apex.",
